# Cloudflare Web Analytics beacon token.
# - Local builds: copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in the token to build
#   your dist with analytics enabled.
# - Deploys: set a GitHub repo Variable named CF_BEACON_TOKEN (Settings → Secrets and variables
#   → Actions → Variables); the deploy workflow passes it to the build.
# Leave it unset and the beacon is simply not injected — which is what forks get.
CF_BEACON_TOKEN=
